00Z","msg":"「百合」一詞是指女性之間戀愛的隱語，其語源有多種說法。最普遍的看法是，1971年，由日本男同性戀雜誌《薔薇族》的編輯長伊藤文學提倡，將「百合族」作為「薔薇族」反義語而起。1982年，因日活浪漫情色電影《水手服 百合族》而廣為流傳，漸成俗語、固定用語。"},{"pid":"22ef591bddb773240578a67fd0e8b272c760b7f5","tid":429191,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T18:28:57.000Z","msg":"呢個台妹真係好顛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09bc3f507887d8c5129999ddeb2d783b2c896064","tid":429191,"uid":6086,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T02:01:56.000Z","msg":"男男係咪叫百足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6153ddc7b8364ec5724f9921717f107b3bf15c6e","tid":429191,"uid":89290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T16:59:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個台妹真係好顛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a38d0b33e1f48d62ad13539bfd5ffc59636b413a","tid":429191,"uid":89290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T17:41:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/09/013933_28ec9904834d6703d48fb5ee47d0fe14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F09%2F013933_28ec9904834d6703d48fb5ee47d0fe14.jpg&h=b0846618&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌呢張第一眼睇我以為佢頭髮係晒前面遮住佢塊面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d071364a10b22e9fb9